OL,3,CMan in wig and uniform seen loitering
OL,4,Coutside schools
OL,6,FPolice are investigating reports of a
OL,7,Fman wearing school uniform and a wig
OL,8,Floitering outside schools in
OL,9,FLincolnshire.
OL,11,FIn one incident, on Friday, 27
OL,12,FSeptember, someone with a "blonde
OL,13,Ffringe and glasses" approached a pupil
OL,14,Fat Priory Ruskin Academy in Grantham.
OL,16,FPolice said it was unclear if it was a
OL,17,Fman or a woman.
OL,19,FA spokesperson said: "We have spoken
OL,20,Fwith the pupil and the school, and the
OL,21,Fschool has issued an email to parents.
