OL,3,CMan in wig and uniform seen loitering
OL,4,Coutside schools
OL,6,F"We would encourage anyone who is
OL,7,Fconcerned about another person
OL,8,Fbehaving suspiciously to make a report
OL,9,Fto the police."
OL,11,FIn a second incident last weej, a
OL,12,Fpupil at Kesteven and Sleaford High
OL,13,FSchool reported seeing a man wearing
OL,14,Fschool uniform and a wig in the Jermyn
OL,15,FStreet area.
OL,17,FHe did not approach anyone and the
OL,18,Fmatter was reported to police.
OL,20,FThe school emailed parents to make
OL,21,Fthem aware of the incident.
